	Druid Magic comes from a harmony with nature.  As a result, the Druid
depends strongly on the forces of the weather.  However, as a result, the
Druid's magic is nearly unstoppable.


  NOTE:  EVERY attack type is affected by weather now.  For example, Fire
does MUCH better when the weather is warm out...

